Package: xtpcmg
Type: Package
Title: Panel Cointegrating Polynomial Regressions via FM-OLS
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: person("Muhammad", "Alkhalaf", email = "muhammedalkhalaf@gmail.com",
    role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"),
    comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0002-2677-9246"))
Description: Implements Group-Mean and Pooled Fully Modified OLS (FM-OLS)
    estimators for panel cointegrating polynomial regressions. The Group-Mean
    FM-OLS follows Wagner and Reichold (2023)
    <doi:10.1080/07474938.2022.2070522>, and the Pooled FM-OLS follows de Jong
    and Wagner (2022) <doi:10.1214/21-AOAS1536>. Both estimators support
    polynomial regressors of degree 2 (quadratic) or 3 (cubic) with optional
    additional I(1) controls, heteroskedasticity and autocorrelation consistent
    (HAC) long-run variance estimation via Bartlett, Parzen, QS, or other
    kernels with automatic Andrews (1991) bandwidth selection. Includes
    turning point analysis with delta-method confidence intervals, coefficient
    heterogeneity analysis, and Swamy (1970) slope homogeneity test.
